h1. servlets 

h2. Purpose

The @servlets@ plug-in enhances with Servlet API with new methods

h2. Examples

Attributes from the [request|controllers], [session|controllers], and [servletContext|controllers] can be accessed with the de-reference operator:

{code:java}
class BookController {
    def find = {
        def findBy = params.findBy
        def foo = request.foo
        def loggedUser = session.logged_user
		...
    }
}
{code}




